title: Facebook's Zuckerberg to meet with lawmakers
text:
Facebook's Zuckerberg met with lawmakers Monday, April 09, 2018 - 01:57 
Facebook chief executive Mark Zuckerberg met with U.S. lawmakers a day before he is due to appear at Congressional hearings over data misuse. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
